      "question": "6. Are there promotional guidelines for KOLs?",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Yes. KOLs must follow branding, content, and compliance guidelines."
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "value": "Misleading or prohibited promotions may result in termination from the program."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
